HEADWORD: Indutive
<hw>In*du"tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>indutus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>induere</ets> to put on. See
<er>Indue</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Covered; -- applied to
